OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FFine throughout, with lengthy
OL,6,Fperiods of sunshine, although this may
OL,7,Fturn rather rather hazy at times under
OL,8,Fhigh cloud. Becoming widely hot,
OL,9,Falthough a little less so in eastern
OL,10,Fcoastal districts. Winds staying light.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FEvening sunny periods will
OL,13,Flead into a dry night, staying very
OL,14,Fwarm for many, especially in larger
OL,15,Fcities. Feeling humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
