OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FMainly fine once again and
OL,6,Fincreasingly hot, with some further
OL,7,Fhazy sunshine, perhaps interrupted in
OL,8,Fthe west by one or two showers or
OL,9,Fpossibly thunderstorms. A little
OL,10,Fbreezier, but humid.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,13,FTemperatures climbing further,
OL,14,Fpotentially becoming very hot by day,
OL,15,Fwith very warm intervening nights.
OL,16,FMainly fine with further sunshine,
OL,17,Fhowever this perhaps triggering
OL,18,Fthunderstorms, mainly Tuesday, and
OL,19,Fperhaps later Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
